title: I havent gotten my 10 year anniversary icon yet
body: i got riot kayle but not the poro icon they said to wait till the 21 to contact so i waited.        {{summoner:11}}  {{summoner:4}}

replies.body: You and many others haven't received the gifts yet, but don't worry the're still being sent out.  Stay up to date at our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) as we continue to send them out.  hang tight!
